metadata.name: Mind Blowing Phantasm #e0001
metadata.description:
A Mind Blowing phantasmagoria from the world of artificial intelligence, generative beyond ours, building on the information that exists, further adding its own learnings to broaden minds in appearance.

All artworks are generated via an Artificial Intelligence algorithm Trained as a Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) through a feed data set of 2000 influences of conceptual beings.
